560x1440px.png", "id": "314658221614549", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_314658224947882_3855311909724896821_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=unxwEs4TmmMQ7kNvgHTZJDD&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCoDIuw195vjtIAgrFAsDbc0qjC3MihDYUJ0j74VMZS8g&oe=66F1508D"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Screenshot-5_2560x1440px.png", "id": "1623928748388173", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569461_1623928751721506_1551295081848351591_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_21J1z8RIRkQ7kNvgH9Dt21&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBSQZH2ivHwK-TOQKTYd-2bnbuSKMbiEHzhZAMonzz_5Q&oe=66F16B1E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-Landscape_2560x1440px.png", "id": "458376827132242", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982552_458376833798908_5317755352769288190_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HxEjO2i9vxEQ7kNvgGXiE0o&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDowcSbyBGbLUNumVByeTdeNukMk44MNOanC8gqPloYUg&oe=66F16330"}, "display_name": "Simulador Soft Skills", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\u00a1Transforma tu potencial y destaca en tu carrera!\nDescubre el simulador dise\u00f1ado para mejorar tus \"Soft Skills\" a trav\u00e9s de varias c\u00e1psulas de formaci\u00f3n esenciales con las que podr\u00e1s:\n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Autoevaluar tus competencias transversales que te ayudar\u00e1n a adaptarte a diferentes entornos de trabajo.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Defender un discurso ante una audiencia para mejorar tu comunicaci\u00f3n y hablar en p\u00fablico.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Entrenar tus fortalezas en un discurso comercial.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Tomar decisiones para desarrollar tus habilidades estrat\u00e9gicas y anal\u00edticas.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Trabajar en equipo para fomentar la colaboraci\u00f3n y la eficiencia del grupo.\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Prepararte para llevar a cabo con \u00e9xito una entrevista de trabajo.", "short_description": "\u00a1Impulsa tus \"Soft Skills\" con nuestro Simulador de Realidad Virtual! Ideal para profesionales que buscan mejorar sus habilidades interpersonales de forma inmersiva, interactiva y efectiva."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Softskills_Cover-Landscape-Padding.png", "id": "3682144288704654", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570314_3682144292037987_5131369632409068623_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9kKJtZAGwR8Q7kNvgEjOBaV&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYChJabA5MPT_2vfwJ7SstOpzigwvvjM0H_3khGDPtQ27g&oe=66F1427A"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1994020534333698", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_1994020537667031_8688105079957652849_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=t3uvfWmRQR4Q7kNvgHfih5q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAC5PKIMuAg1egW1AM-dW7lZNnHZczvbIElG4H3_s2_5Q&oe=66F16243"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1247184912914732", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1247184916248065_2567077078745571082_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=H3M-ubJmUawQ7kNvgGV7oFv&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDkAZ1WvvxzB_ducJD92LSBMbFWJZp_n2izkgqXsxq4ZQ&oe=66F13833"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "1187254515612530", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974888_1187254518945863_7395065576696775988_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DDaI_l25GIUQ7kNvgHW16EE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBrGvfIzBZeicBHmpnXp3vUIw3G-ICEumaL8NQwlGtfxQ&oe=66F160C0"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1151595012723300", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982662_1151595016056633_8079137566055371486_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid