fe0f\u20e3 Defend a speech in front of an audience to improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Train your strengths in a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Make decisions to develop your strategic and analytical skills.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Work as part of a team to foster collaboration and group efficiency.", "short_description": "Boost your \"Soft Skills\" with our Virtual Reality Simulator! \n\nComposed of 5 training capsules to: \n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Self-assess your transversal competences.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Defend a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Speed up decision making.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Promote teamwork.\n\nIdeal for professionals looking to improve their interpersonal skills in an immersive, interactive and effective way!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YgLr1k0RyqgQ7kNvgFfzBR8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA-AKpNpSNxN7xNs8fn-Y38BivI57JYhM8UKHnc9NMNkQ&oe=66F153E9"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1001238441075007", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_1001238447741673_2783185145492224256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VPLr57sqJMsQ7kNvgHrFGWc&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD3yaK7UJfXZ4PEHTo0c4E63A7VJfB_CFCtmQJOvDojgA&oe=66F16CAF"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "837105901661785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_837105904995118_1711704673161247418_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=31Q8JE8GjcMQ7kNvgGl8VYC&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB5s5fiMQp9yDO7HCgWGg78O9WOsIPxhXwnlfXSbkHhKQ&oe=66F161F3"}, 